eco\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2015|9|17}}\n| ProdCode        = 1031-073\n| Viewers         = 1.50<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/09/18/thursday-cable-ratings-thursday-night-football-leads-the-night-teen-mom-ii-project-runway-thursday-night-smackdown-college-football-more/468795/|title=Thursday Cable Ratings: 'Thursday Night Football' Leads the Night + 'Teen Mom II' + 'Project Runway', 'Thursday Night Smackdown', 'College Football' & More|last=Dixon|first=Dani|work=TV by the Numbers|date=September 18, 2015|accessdate=September 18, 2015}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = Steven helps Sadie with an act for the annual Beach-a-Palooza talent show.\n| LineColor       = 91ECDD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 70\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 17\n| Title           = Catch and Release\n| DirectedBy      = Kat Morris {{small|(supervising)}}<br />Jasmin Lai {{small|(art)}}\n| WrittenBy       = Hilary Florido and Lauren Zuke\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2015|9|24}}\n| ProdCode        = 1031-070\n| Viewers         = 1.39<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-100-thursday-cable-originals-9-24-2015.html|title=SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 100 Thursday Cable Originals & Network Update: 9.24.2015|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=September 25, 2015|accessdate=September 25, 2015}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = The Crystal Gems finally capture Peridot, but Steven suspects that she has information that the Crystal Gems need to know and attempts to learn what it is, allowing her to live in his bathroom.\n| LineColor       = 91ECDD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 71\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 18\n| Title           = When It Rains\n| DirectedBy      = Joe Johnston {{small|(supervising)}}<br />Jasmin Lai {{small|(art)}}\n| WrittenBy       = Lamar Abrams and Katie Mitroff\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2015|10|1}}\n| ProdCode        = 1031-071\n| Viewers         = 1.36<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.