, 2015|accessdate=October 16, 2015}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = Peridot gets carried away with Gem gossip and reveals something about Amethyst, unintentionally offending her.\n| LineColor       = 91ECDD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 74\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 21\n| Title           = [[The Answer (Steven Universe)|The Answer]]\n| DirectedBy      = Joe Johnston {{small|(supervising)}}<br />Jasmin Lai {{small|(art)}}\n| WrittenBy       = Lamar Abrams and Katie Mitroff\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|4}}\n| ProdCode        = 1031-075\n| Viewers         = 1.38<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-monday-cable-originals-network-update-1-4-2016.html|title=SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 150 Monday Cable Originals & Network Update: 1.4.2016|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=January 6, 2016|accessdate=January 6, 2016}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = Garnet tells Steven the story of how Ruby and Sapphire first met and joined the Crystal Gems.<br />This episode was nominated for an [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Short Form Animated Program|Emmy Award for Outstanding Short-Form Animation]].\n| LineColor       = 91ECDD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 75\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 22\n| Title           = Steven's Birthday\n| DirectedBy      = Joe Johnston {{small|(supervising)}}<br />Jasmin Lai {{small|(art)}}\n| WrittenBy       = Lamar Abrams and Katie Mitroff\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|5}}\n| ProdCode        = 1031-079\n| Viewers         = 1.35<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-tuesday-cable-originals-network-update-1-5-2016.html|title=SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 150 Tuesday Cable Originals & Network Update: 1.5.2016|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=January 6, 2016|accessdate=January 6, 2016}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary    = While celebrating his fourteenth birthday with the Gems, Greg, and Connie, Steven takes on a more adult form using his sha