 Announcement for Volume 2: The Return|url=http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Steven-Universe-Volume-2/22209|website=tvshowsondvd.com|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429131541/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Steven-Universe-Volume-2/22209|archivedate=April 29, 2016|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"background:#94C9D9\" |\n| ''The Heart of the Crystal Gems''\n| 12\n| 132\n| 98/99, 107, 120, 130, 146, 147, 148, 149, 150, 151/152\n| {{n/a}}\n| August 14, 2018<ref>{{cite web|title=\"Steven Universe\" Returns for Five-Night Event Monday, July 2 on Cartoon Network|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2018/06/18/steven-universe-returns-for-five-night-event-monday-july-2-on-cartoon-network-208412/20180618cartoon01/|website=The Futon Critic|accessdate=June 18, 2018|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"background:#94c980\" |\n| ''[[Steven Universe: The Movie]]''\n| {{n/a}}\n| 90\n| {{n/a}}\n| ''Behind the Curtain'' documentary,<br>animatics, commentary\n| November 12, 2019<ref>{{cite web |title=Steven Universe The Movie DVD |url=https://www.rightstufanime.com/Steven-Universe-The-Movie-DVD |website=Right Stuf |accessdate=14 August 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Region 4===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" |Title\n! Episode count\n! Running time (minutes)\n! Episodes\n! Extra features\n! Release date\n|-\n! colspan=\"7\" | Season releases\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FF5E6D\" |\n| ''The Complete First Season''\n| 52\n| 572\n| 1\u201335, 37, 36, 38-47, 49-53\n| Pilot episode\n| May 4, 2016<ref name=\"madman.com.au\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"background:#91ECDD\" |\n| ''The Complete Second Sason''\n| 26\n| 286\n| 54-55, 48, 56-78\n| {{n/a}}\n| May 24, 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.madman.com.au/catalogue/view/38325/steven-universe-season-2-bluray|title=Steven Universe Season 2 (Blu-Ray)|website=Madman Entertainment|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517233206/https://www.madman.com.au/catalogue/view/38325/steven-u